.subPage.bigrock-blog.animated
  .subHeader.container-fluid
    .row
      .col-xs-3
        %a{:href => "/portfolio"} < back

      .col-xs-6.text-center
        %span.title BigRock Blog

      .col-xs-3


  .subPageContent.container
    .row
      .col-xs-12.logoWrp.text-center
        %img.img-responsive{:src => "../images/bigrock-blog-logo.gif"}


    .row
      .col-sm-12.introWrp
        .titleWrp.text-center
          %p.title
            %span Overview

        %p.para.text-justify
          BigRock blog was build on WordPress. The nearest simple theme was chosen and skinning and customization was build on top of it. For most part I had to add required widgets and style the pages as required according the given design.

        %p.btnWrp.text-center
          %a.btn.btn-success.btn-flat.checkInAction{:href => "http://www.bigrock.com/blog", :target => "_blank", :rel => "nofollow"} Checkout BigRock Blog

        .infoWrp.row
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.roleWrp
            %p.title My Role:
            %p.role
              HTML / CSS, WordPress Themes

          .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.platformWrp
            %p.title Platforms:
            %ul.platforms
              %li.pull-left.fa.fa-desktop.active
              %li.pull-left.fa.fa-tablet
              %li.pull-left.fa.fa-mobile

    .row
      .col-sm-12.snapshotWrp
        .titleWrp.text-center
          %p.title
            %span Snapshots

        .snapshots
          .row-fluid
            %img.img-responsive{:src => ""}
          .row-fluid
            %img.img-responsive{:src => ""}
          .row-fluid
            %img.img-responsive{:src => ""}